{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0004","text":"蓬萊依舊在那裏 如何踏進 你那領土","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["目標","距離","渴望"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["蓬萊","依舊","領土"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,3,2,2,5,5,0,0,2,4,5,5,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pung4","loi4","ji1","gau6","zoi6","naa5","leoi5","jyu4","ho4","daap6","zeon3","nei5","naa5","ling5","tou2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"蓬萊","pos":"PROPN"},{"text":"依舊","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"那裏","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"如何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"踏進","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那","pos":"DET"},{"text":"領土","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以神話中的仙境『蓬萊』比喻目標，『依舊在那裏』強調目標的固定與不可及，『如何』引出疑問。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0005","text":"對地對天 一日還是活着","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["生命","希望","渴望"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["活着","盼望"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,2,4,3,3,2,0,2,2,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["deoi3","dei6","deoi3","tin1","jat1","jat6","waan4","si6","wut6","zoek6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"對","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"地","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"對","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"還是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"活着","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"『對地對天』表達一種廣泛的生命狀態，『還是活着』帶有堅韌的意味，為後續的盼望鋪墊。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0006","text":"都盼有生一天 走到你身邊","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["希望","渴望","目標"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["盼","一天","身邊"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,5,3,3,3,9,4,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dou1","paan3","jau5","sang1","jat1","tin1","zau2","dou3","nei5","san1","bin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"盼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有生","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"一天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"走到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"身邊","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『都盼』、『有生一天』、『走到你身邊』，直接表達了對與目標對象相遇的強烈渴望。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0007","text":"遙遠 怎樣及吻你遠","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["距離","渴望","不可能"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["遙遠","怎樣","吻你遠"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,9,2,2,5,5,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jiu4","jyun5","zam2","joeng6","kap6","man5","nei5","jyun5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"遙遠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"怎樣","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"及","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"遠","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"『遙遠』與『遠』的疊加，『怎樣及吻你遠』是一種誇張的說法，強調距離的遙不可及。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0008","text":"地平就算再遠 總在人面前","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["希望","目標","存在"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["地平","就算","面前"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,2,4,4,5,9,2,0,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dei6","ping4","zau6","syun3","zoi3","jyun5","zung2","zoi6","jan4","min6","cin4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"地","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"平","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就算","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"遠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"總在","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"面前","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『地平線』是永恆的目標，『就算再遠，總在人面前』，表達了目標雖然遙遠但始終存在，給予人希望。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
