{"id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0015","text":"無緣站近些 才後退一步","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["緣分","距離","退縮"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["無緣","後退"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,2,3,0,2,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mou4","jyun4","zaam6","gan6","se1","coi4","hau6","teoi3","jat1","bou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"無緣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"站","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"近些","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"才","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"後退","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一步","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"『無緣站近些』點出無法靠近的原因，『才後退一步』與前面的『行前幾步』形成對比，表達一種無奈的放棄。"},"source":{"title":"地平線","artists":["官恩娜"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_585","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6Y5oGp5aic_NTg1_0016","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
